title: Ep. #142 | Catching Up: Seori
description:
Solo artist Seori sits with Eric in Los Angeles to chat about her journey from posting covers on YouTube to being a full blown musician on the rise. Merely days after her performance at 88rising's Head in the Clouds festival, Seori reflects on her growth, her album, and where she hopes to go from here.
